  "detailed_description": "Control a variety of robots and destroy invaders from outer space in order to save the destroyed earth!<br><br>\"GAIA Survivors\" is a 'Shoot 'Em Up' type sci-fi rogue-lite casual game with a retro-futuristic worldview.<br><br>・Control robots equipped with a variety of weapons and survive epic battles!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463250/extras/8ad9481bb15de22c5f8a807c4fe17d9c.avif?t=1696566098\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>・Power up your robots with crystals collected during battles and defeat stronger enemies!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463250/extras/85fce69d95490559991e026dd0202c54.avif?t=1696566098\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463250/extras/25fc24ba24c36077d44c1a0e546efb91.avif?t=1696566098\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>・Develop items with the ores you bring back to your home for more power ups!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463250/extras/bb30f8b070451d65c6ccc4d4f2f3419a.avif?t=1696566098\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463250/extras/8fb7d7175d09101bff0c3ea890ecb22b.avif?t=1696566098\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>・Unlock new weapons and robots, and venture into unknown stages!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463250/extras/a8d72ba9af297fdd88afdab35b43246b.avif?t=1696566098\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463250/extras/f612d94a0dc6561604f116074aab2627.avif?t=1696566098\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463250/extras/d95dd6f70e3418fbb9b21f89a99fb241.avif?t=1696566098\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463250/extras/a0986cfbc830ce35b3b4b99206ccc39f.avif?t=1696566098\" width=480 height=270 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Control a variety of robots and destroy invaders from outer space in order to save the destroyed earth!<br><br>\"GAIA Survivors\" is a 'Shoot 'Em Up' type sci-fi rogue-lite casual game with a retro-futuristic worldview.<br><br>・Control robots equipped with a variety of weapons and survive epic battles!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463250/extras/8ad9481bb15de22c5f8a807c4fe17d9c.avif?t=1696566098\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>・Power up your robots with crystals collected during battles and defeat stronger enemies!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463250/extras/85fce69d95490559991e026dd0202c54.avif?t=1696566098\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463250/extras/25fc24ba24c36077d44c1a0e546efb91.avif?t=1696566098\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>・Develop items with the ores you bring back to your home for more power ups!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463250/extras/bb30f8b070451d65c6ccc4d4f2f3419a.avif?t=1696566098\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463250/extras/8fb7d7175d09101bff0c3ea890ecb22b.avif?t=1696566098\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>・Unlock new weapons and robots, and venture into unknown stages!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463250/extras/a8d72ba9af297fdd88afdab35b43246b.avif?t=1696566098\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akama